                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-196-off1106 t18270913-196-crimeloc1108"></join>. On the 7th of August I went out about eleven o'clock, and left the key in my door - I returned in a quarter of an hour, and found the key had been turned, and my shawl gone off my table - I saw it again at Mr. Blitz's door, on the Friday following - I know it by a darn, which is my own work - I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>
